import React from 'react'
import {Card, CardContent, Typography} from '@material-ui/core'
import {Field, Form, Formik} from 'formik'
import {CheckboxWithLabel, TextField} from 'formik-material-ui'

export default function NewEvent() {
    return(
            <Card>
                <CardContent>
                    <Formik initialValues={{
                        title: '',
                        description: '',
                        closedSpace: false,
                        concurrency:0
                    }}
                    onSumbit={() => {}}>
                    <Form autocomplete="off"> 
                    <Field name= "title" component={TextField} label="Event Title"/>
                    <Field name= "description" component={TextField} label="Description"/>
                    <Field name= "state" type="checkbox" component={CheckboxWithLabel} label={{label: 'does the event take place in a closed space?'}}/>
                    <Field name= "concurrency" type="number" component={TextField} label="Concurrency"/>
                    </Form>

                    </Formik>
                </CardContent>
            </Card>
    )
}
